org.sosy_lab.solver.visitors

Class RecursiveFormulaVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sosy_lab.solver.visitors.FormulaVisitor<Void>
      • org.sosy_lab.solver.visitors.RecursiveFormulaVisitor

  • public abstract class RecursiveFormulaVisitor
extends FormulaVisitor<Void>
    Formula visitor which visits every element exactly once.

    Allows to traverse DAG-like formulas without an exponential explosion.
